## Code Simplification Report

### No Changes Needed

Code is already clean. No simplifications applied.

The PR itself already contains several deliberate simplification passes:

- **`backend/models.py`** — Extracted `_validate_data_size` and `_validate_open_questions` as shared helpers, eliminating duplicated validation logic across `ThingCreate` and `ThingUpdate`.
- **`backend/routers/nudges.py`** — Merged `_RECURRING_KEYS`, `_ONESHOT_KEYS`, `_ALL_DATE_KEYS`, and `_KEY_LABELS` into a single `_DATE_KEY_CONFIG` dict, cutting ~20 lines and one lookup per key.
- **`frontend/src/components/BriefingPanel.tsx`** — Merged `FINDING_TYPE_ICONS` and `FINDING_TYPE_COLORS` into `FINDING_TYPE_CONFIG`.
- **`frontend/src/components/ChatPanel.tsx`** — Extracted `ExpandChevron` component (used in 3 places) and lifted `STAGES` to a module-level constant to eliminate repeated `indexOf` calls in the streaming indicator.
- **`frontend/src/components/Sidebar.tsx`** — Moved `TYPE_ORDER`, `FALLBACK_LABELS`, and `SEVERITY_COLORS` to module scope instead of re-declaring them inside two `useMemo` callbacks; replaced a nested ternary for severity colors with a dict lookup.
- **`frontend/src/store.ts`** — Removed explicit object reconstruction in `fetchBriefing` (API response shape already matches store type).

No remaining complexity, redundancy, or naming issues found.

